    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In the case for immobile turreted actors (i.e. all base defenses) `AttackFollow.AttackActivity` runs continuously instead of sequencing other activities.  When the stop order is issued the `AttackFollow` changes its target to invalid, but the activity doesn't detect this because it keeps its own internal copy that isn't updated.\n"
